Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:10.37,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Let me fulfill your small wish together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:15.71,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Ah, of course they’ll be with us as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:51.41,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}I see... So Armony's transmutations weren't failures all this time. They were only dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:54.42,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fs25}She could have become a once-in-a-generation alchemist...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:59.42,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,When you die, you're dead; that's the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:24.21,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:56.65,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,It's okay to cry, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:00.32,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Don’t be ridiculous. Let’s go!
